    "title": "Wish you had a personal AI to help you find the most relevant GovCo...",
    "date": "2025-01-17",
    "content": "Wish you had a personal AI to help you find the most relevant GovCon events (without wading through the noise)?\"\n\"\nThat‚Äôs exactly what we built‚Äîand we did it in under a week, via the ‚ÄúAccelerated AI Adoption‚Äù methodology I use to help SMBs and enterprises set bold goals and get their 10x faster, with some help from generative AI.\n\"\nTogether with Ron Jones (CEO G2Xchange), we set out to tackle a simple question:¬†‚ÄúHow do we match people to GovCon events that actually matter to them?‚Äù\n\"\nThe result is¬†GovConEvents AI:\n\"\n1.\tMatches¬†the entire G2X GovCon event calendar (one of their many proprietary \"data assets,\" a perfect complement to generative AI) to your LinkedIn profile;\n\"\n2.\tRecommends the top events for your background, skills, and interests; and\n\"\n3.\tLets you add your own events with a single click‚Äîmaking the tool more useful for everyone.\n\"\n[All free, no sensitive data stored, and (most importantly) no more sifting through dozens of irrelevant events.]\n\"\nWhy this matters:\n\"\n‚Ä¢\tGovCon thrives on authentic connections‚Äîthis gives you a quick and easy way to find¬†your¬†next valuable networking opportunity.\n\"\n‚Ä¢\tIt showcases what‚Äôs possible when you combine subject-matter expertise with agile AI development‚Äîdelivering real value, fast.\n\"\nIf you try it out, let me know how it goes, especially if it leads you to an event you might have otherwise missed. If we see enough people benefitting, we‚Äôll fold an enhanced version into the G2X platform later this year.\n\"\nCheck it out:¬†https://govcon.events\n\"\n1.\tDrop in your LinkedIn URL\n\"\n2.\tGet your event recommendations\n\"\n3.\tStart networking smarter\n\"\nHuge thanks to Ron for helping me prove how quickly we can bring a real AI solution to market. \n\"\n\"On to the next experiment!",
