    "title": "\"What if your search engine could stop you from making a bad decisi...",
    "date": "2024-11-26",
    "content": "What if your search engine could stop you from making a bad decision before you even knew you were about to make it?\n\"\nWe've become so accustomed to typing queries into search boxes that we've forgotten a crucial truth: the most valuable insights often come from being asked the right question at the right time.\n\"\nI believe the next evolution in AI isn't about better answers‚Äîit's about better questions. And it's closer than you think.\n\"\nIn this article, I explore:\n\"\n- Why our expectations in re reactive internet search is holding back business decision-making\n- How proactive AI questioning will transform how leaders work\n- What this future actually looks like in practice\n\"\nAfter spending the last two years building in this space, I'm convinced this shift will fundamentally change how executives access and use information.\n\"\nCurious to hear your thoughts: What questions do you wish your technology would ask you?\n\"\n\"h/t Mark Amtower for helping me get this into shape!",
