    "id": "post-2024-11-16-7263585250360930305",
    "title": "If you've spent some time on the AI frontier since ChatGPT was laun...",
    "date": "2024-11-16",
    "content": "If you've spent some time on the AI frontier since ChatGPT was launched, I STRONGLY encourage you to spend some quality time with o1-preview‚Äîwhether via Chat or the dev playground (platform dot openai dot com).\"\n\"\nPop in a codebase, a complex contract, or even a bunch of transcripts from meetings you were in, and just¬†play¬†with it!\n\"\nEven though o1 outputs text just like any other model, it‚Äôs qualitatively different from what we‚Äôve gotten used to with LLMs over the past two years. \n\"\nIt provides responses that verge on proactive; it seems capable of deriving genuinely insightful information that goes beyond compression. At times, it even ‚Äúfeels‚Äù like it‚Äôs drawing from out-of-distribution contexts.\n\"\nPractically speaking, for me, over the past 2 months, its enabled outcomes that would have been prohibitively expensive in terms of time (or wages for, say, a SME contractor).\n\"\nPersonally, the main bottleneck is my own limited attention. I have to concentrate super hard to ensure I‚Äôm fully understanding what it returns before I take action. It‚Äôs honestly kind of uncomfortable because I‚Äôm used to learning quickly, but o1-preview is pushing me to operate right at the limits of my knowledge. Especially with coding, I‚Äôve had to focus‚Äîintensely and for unbroken periods of time‚Äîto digest its insights. \n\"\nIt feels similar to how I had to approach the content of my most challenging undergrad courses ‚Äî the cognitive equivalent of going for a squat PR, except the o1 \"curriculum\" latent in our chats is entirely bespoke and based on my goals!\n\"\n\"I don't say this lightly: In o1, there are sparks of superintelligence, truly. You can see them for yourself, right now.",
    "excerpt": "If you've spent some time on the AI frontier since ChatGPT was launched, I STRONGLY encourage you to spend some quality time with o1-preview‚Äîwhether via Chat...",
