    "content": "Iterating at the speed of thought...\"\n\"\nBig news ‚Äî¬†OpenAI, Anthropic, and Perplexity have released with MacOS apps! \n\"\nWanted to share a little demo: by piping data between systems like ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, and superwhisper, I was able to, just now:\n\"\n- Rapidly research cutting-edge topics in precision medicine\n- Draft emails and poems weaving the content together\n- Create an interactive application from scratch\n- Iterate on the app's design based on AI feedback...\n\"\nAll of this in around 12 minutes.\n\"\nAs models become more powerful and multimodal, and integrations enable seamless data transfer, we're getting closer to \"brain-computer interface\" speeds.\n\"\nSoon, transforming ideas into reality with AI will be near-instantaneous!\n\"\nCheck out the full video to see it all in action:\n\"\n\"https://lnkd.in/eHaHBC4i",
