    "id": "post-2024-10-08-7249450988820918272",
    "title": "ChatGPT or Claude?\"\n\"\"\n\"I'm asked this question a lot",
    "date": "2024-10-08",
    "content": "ChatGPT or Claude?\"\n\"\nI'm asked this question a lot...\n\"\nAnd while, on one hand, it is a bit like Coke vs. Pepsi, on the other, there are good reasons to prefer one over the other, even at the level of a particular task.\n\"\nHere's how I think* about it:\n\"\nGiven the task-at-hand, would you rather delegate it to someone who got 800 on the Math portion of the SAT? \n\"\nOr someone who scored 800 on Verbal?\n\"\nIf it's the former (say, you wish you had a data scientist to crunch the giant CRM export you just generated before the next exec report-out), Chat‚Äîespecially with Code Interpreter‚Äîmight be the right tool.\n\"\nIf it's the latter (say, you need help drafting a follow-up email based on your most recent meeting transcript), ask Claude.\n\"\n\"*this is subject to change as the tech evolves...and that's one of the reasons why I continue to pay for and continuously experiment with both!",
