    "date": "2024-07-26",
    "content": "Sama announced voice AI is rolling out over the next few weeks.\"\n\"\nAre you ready?\n\"\nTrue voice-to-voice will be a big deal, maybe bigger than the ChatGPT launch.\n\"\nThe fact that I could tap that icon from my lock screen and immediately start speaking with my computer is, in and of itself, incredible. And then it'll only get better over time. \n\"\nFirst, with integrations and your private data, the quality of the conversations will go up as it gets better at knowing more about you. \n\"\nThen eventually, and I don't know how long this could take, I suspect it'll be years or even a decade, it'll start taking actions on your behalf. \n\"\nAnd with each release, each step change and backend model capabilities, every single conversation you have with this thing will just get better and better and better. \n\"\nThe implications for business, the consumer internet, and all the interesting knock-on effects that might happen as a result of this fundamental shift in personal computing are really worth thinking about. \n\"\nLike the mainframe to the PC or the PC to mobile.\n\"\n\"No typing, no tapping, no scrolling or searching - just talk.",
