    "title": "How to integrate #generativeAI into an enterprise:\"\n\"\"\n\"1",
    "date": "2024-07-18",
    "content": "How to integrate #generativeAI into an enterprise:\"\n\"\n1. Give everyone general purpose tools (SOTA foundation models + ability to easily digitize their environment, e.g., superwhisper, Loom, Fireflies.ai and/or the compliant substitutes),\n\"\n2. Make power users more powerful: hands-on training to guide them toward increasingly sophisticated delegation of clerical tasks (+ unsticking information gained from their self-directed experimentation via qualitative interviews & product analytics, if feasible),\n\"\n3. Encode expertise into streamlined (\"artisanal\")  software (ask good questions and pipe the answers into prompts you can build web apps around and make available to more conservative colleagues), and\n\"\n\"4. Raise your expectations for the organization by pursuing more ambitious, well-defined goals in less time (ordered desire + constraints beget innovation and growth ‚Äî¬†AI can be a source of leverage, but there needs to be a forcing function in place for rigorous use and thorough adoption).",
