    "content": "Hire an AI Assistant to Be Your Daily Preparation Coach:\"\n\"\nIn this video tutorial, you'll learn how to create an AI-powered voice assistant that calls you every morning and evening to help you prepare for your day and reflect on your progress, just like Marshall Goldsmith's famous daily check-in process.\n\"\nUsing tools like:\n- Vapi (YC W21) (voice assistant platform)\n- Anthropic's Claude (AI model)\n- Replit (for scheduling)\n- Make (for email integration)\n- Descript and ElevenLabs (for voice cloning)\n\"\nYou'll be guided through the steps to set up your own \"Moneypenny\" assistant who will call you at scheduled times, have a conversation to identify your priorities and plans, and send you a follow-up email with a summary and action items.\n\"\nBy the end of this 30-minute tutorial, you'll have your own AI coach to help you stay on track and focused on what matters most. Try it out and let me know if you have any questions!\n\"\n\"https://lnkd.in/esc2CEc7",
