    "date": "2024-06-10",
    "content": "Here's the deal ‚Äî¬†REAL digital transformation doesn't have to be expensive, time-consuming, or require an army of consultants.\"\n\"\nWhat if instead of wading through months of PPT, you could instead get results immediately by working with a lean, mean boutique shop that knows how to use generative AI tools across industries and workflows, solves real problems with urgency, and energizes staff?\n\"\nDigital transformation is possible, but, in 2024, how you get there looks different, thanks to this new generation of tech...\n\"\nBefore AI, shipping a 0-1 IT milestone could take months + a team of engineers, designers, product managers, and scrum masters (especially in an enterprise setting).\n\"\nBut now, that time-to-first-magic-moment can be compressed dramatically ‚Äî¬†all you need is hyper-focused team (maybe just one person!) who pays close attention to user needs and uses SOTA models to build stuff that works NOW.\n\"\nAs a buyer/executive, consider this your invitation to raise your expectations when working with outside experts on AI integration & digital transformation initiatives...\n\"\nThat's why I don't charge for discovery ‚Äî¬†AI-native firms like mine can focus on selling outcomes, not billable hours.\n\"\nAre you interested in going 0-1 on enterprise AI integrations in hours, not months?\n\"\n(And keeping your investors, board, and employees satisfied in the process...)\n\"\n\"Send me a DM.",
