    "title": "My 4-step process to ‚ÄúElectrify‚Äù businesses with generative AI: \"\n\"...",
    "date": "2024-04-25",
    "content": "My 4-step process to ‚ÄúElectrify‚Äù businesses with generative AI: \"\n \n(developed after 20+ successful AI integration projects) \n \nüéØ ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùü≠: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùó£ùóºùó∂ùóªùòÅ ùóï (ùòÑùóµùó≤ùóøùó≤ ùòÜùóºùòÇ ùòÑùóÆùóªùòÅ ùòÅùóº ùó¥ùóº) \n \nBegin by envisioning your desired outcome. \n \n‚Ä¢ Actionable AI integration starts with clarity over the desired outcome. \n‚Ä¢ Where are we currently (Point A) & where do we want to be (Point B) \n‚Ä¢ A strategic goal provides a lens for problem identification, AI tool selection, and decision-making. \n \nSet good goals. THEN, use AI to get there 10 times faster. \n \nüß± ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùüÆ: ùóóùóøùóÆùòÑ ùóÆ ùóïùóπùòÇùó≤ùóΩùóøùó∂ùóªùòÅ \n \nThe objective is to identify the highest leverage AI opportunity (use-case). \n \n‚Ä¢ Using tools like Miro, I draw an end-to-end map of the company's processes. \n‚Ä¢ This helps visualize the workflow, making it easy to identify where AI can be most useful‚Äîin other words, ‚Äúwhere to install the first AI-as-electricity outlet‚Äù. \n‚Ä¢ Here, we use the goals we set above to guide the decision-making. \n \nPost blueprinting, the AI opportunity (almost) jumps out at you! \n \nüïµüèª ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùüØ: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùóîùóú ùòÉùóÆùóªùó¥ùòÇùóÆùóøùó± \n \nSuccessful AI transformation requires leadership to drive the change.  \n \n‚Ä¢ AI vanguard is your leader who oversees the AI integration process. \n‚Ä¢ He/She is equipped with resources, authority, and support. \n‚Ä¢ They have the license to experiment, implement, and scale AI across the business. \n \nThis role is crucial. Choose your champion wisely. \n \n‚ö°Ô∏è ùó¶ùòÅùó≤ùóΩ ùü∞: ùó¶ùòÅùóÆùóøùòÅ ùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùóîùóú \n \nNow, we build the AI solution that we identified in step 2. \n \n‚Ä¢ The nature of the solution will be specific to your business. \n‚Ä¢ One-size fits all approach doesn‚Äôt work. \n‚Ä¢ I recommend approaching every problem separately and designing tailored AI solutions. \n \nSome solutions: Customized prompt library, Claude Pro + Fireflies AI + Superwhisper, artisanal AI software. \n \nThere are many possible types of solutions.  \n \nNature of the solution doesn‚Äôt matter, as long as it works! \n \nI‚Äôve implemented this process across 20+ businesses in 10+ industries. \n \nAnd we‚Äôve created a long-lasting impact. \n \nSo, I know it works. \n \n\"Would you like me to expand on any of the steps?",
