    "date": "2024-04-23",
    "content": "3 tips for integrating AI into your company culture: \"\n \n(and inspire your team to become AI-powered) \n \nüí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùü≠: ùó¶ùóΩùóºùóªùòÄùóºùóø ùóîùóú ùó∂ùóªùòÅùóøùóºùó±ùòÇùó∞ùòÅùóºùóøùòÜ ùòÑùóºùóøùó∏ùòÄùóµùóºùóΩùòÄ \n \nA workshop is more than just an event. \n \nIt‚Äôs a signal to your team that AI is an important deal.  \nWhen your team witnesses leaders embracing AI, they‚Äôll do the same. \nAnd an AI workshop is the perfect way to execute this! \n \nRemember: You are only one ‚ÄúAHA‚Äù moment away from being AI-powered. \n \n \nüí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùüÆ: ùó®ùòÄùó≤ ùóüùóºùóºùó∫ ùòÉùó∂ùó±ùó≤ùóºùòÄ ùòÅùóº ùòÄùóΩùóøùó≤ùóÆùó± ùóîùóú ùòÄùòÇùó∞ùó∞ùó≤ùòÄùòÄ \n \nSuccess with AI spreads like wildfire. \n \nSo, you must be prepared with a mechanism that allows the wildfire :) \nEducate people on Loom videos & incentivize sharing them. \nShow, don‚Äôt tell. \nSet an example by creating looms yourself & coaching a few people 1:1. \n \nBefore you know it, your entire team will be using AI in ways you never imagined. \n \n \nüí° ùóßùó∂ùóΩ ùüØ: ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùóîùóú ùòÉùóÆùóªùó¥ùòÇùóÆùóøùó± \n \n This person will be in charge of the AI bandwagon. \n \n \nHe/She will experiment with new AI solutions & make them accessible.  \nHe/She will include AI as part of every weekly review.  \nHe/She will work directly with you to identify the biggest AI opportunities. \n \nIncentivize this properly, and your AI vanguard‚Äôs intrinsic motivation will ensure the AI wave spreads through your organization! \n \n*** \n \nIndividually, these tips work great. \n \nBut combined, they‚Äôll create a long-lasting change in the business. \n \nIt only takes 1 or 2 solutions. \n \nAfter that, your business will never work without AI. \n \nThink about this: Have humans ever lived without electricity after they experienced it? \n \nYou will sit back and enjoy the show! \n \n*** \n \nPS ‚Äì Have you conducted AI introductory workshops for your teams yet? \n \nI‚Äôve done 20+ workshops that my clients have found super valuable. \n \nWe solve one narrow problem. \nWe identify early adopters. \nWe set the stage for AI. \n \n \nIf you‚Äôre interested, DM me ‚ÄúAI workshop‚Äù. \n \n\"We‚Äôll talk about how we can design one for you :)",
