    "date": "2024-04-22",
    "content": "If things go right, AI will free up 50% of your time.  \"\n \nBut it doesn‚Äôt help if you don‚Äôt answer this question: \n \n‚ÄúWhat will we do with all this free time?‚Äù \n \nHere are 4 ways I like to use the surplus time: \n \n1/ Creation \n‚Ü≥ Tinker with technology, experiment, and start building something. \n \n2/ Relation \n‚Ü≥ Invest time to nurture strong & meaningful relationships \n \n3/ Contemplation \n‚Ü≥ Process your thoughts away from the digital world (and become more mindful) \n \n4/ Orchestration \n‚Ü≥ Zoom out and think ‚ÄúHow can I work better with all the tools & machines?‚Äù \n \nAI & technology exist to help us become more human. \n \nTo explore our curiosities on the frontier. \nTo build more meaningful connections. \nTo make wise & mindful decisions. \nTo have more fun! \n \nOnce we start believing in this new way of work, \n \nAdopting AI and welcoming it into our business (or life) becomes easier. \n \nI‚Äôve seen it for myself. \n \nI‚Äôve seen it for my clients too. \n \n\"There‚Äôs no going back :)",
