    "content": "I'm looking for a skilled LinkedIn copywriter or ghostwriter to produce 20 high-quality posts per month, derived from my raw content (videos, meeting transcripts, presentations).\"\n\"\nKey details:\n- Benchmark cost: $1,000/month for 20 posts (am open to outcome-based comp. as well if you're confident you can deliver)\n- Posts require my approval\n- Expectation is text, but open to multimedia posts (I have lots of raw material from meeting recordings, monologues, etc.)\n- Flexible on process (previously used Taplio to schedule + async comms via Slack & Loom previously)\n- Referral bonus: 30% of first month ($300) if you recommend someone I end up working with\n\"\nI help executive teams set and pursue good goals on the frontier of their industry, & get there 10X faster with AI. \n\"\nHave served clients over the past year and change w/ engagements that were mostly focused on one or the other, but am looking to bring this together cohesively going forward and continue to use LinkedIn as top-of-funnel channel.\n\"\nHigh expectations - I know what's possible with AI. If you're an excellent writer who delivers great results quickly, let's talk!\n\"\n\"Reach out directly here or at christian (at) gsdat (dot) work.",
