    "date": "2024-04-18",
    "content": "How to identify ‚ÄúAI as Thought Partner‚Äù opportunities for your business? \"\n \n(And use AI to assist you in making high-quality decisions) \n \nAI is excellent at solving the ‚Äúblank page‚Äù problem. \n \nThe dynamic nature of business means: \n \n‚Üí You‚Äôll face situations you‚Äôve never faced before \n‚Üí You‚Äôll face problems you‚Äôve never solved before \n‚Üí You‚Äôll face decisions you‚Äôve never made before \n \nTo confidently make these decisions, you need to research. \n \nAI acts as an on-ramp to the frontier. \n \nReducing your research time. \n \nBy a significant margin. \n \nHere are 2 questions that‚Äôll help you reveal these opportunities: \n \nùóßùóµùóºùòÇùó¥ùóµùòÅ ùó£ùóÆùóøùòÅùóªùó≤ùóø ùó§ùòÇùó≤ùòÄùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùü≠: \n‚Ü≥ What's something that you know you need to figure out, but you don't even know where to start? \n \n[Tip: Compile a list of problems that are outside of your area of expertise and you keep pushing to number two on your to do list. If you‚Äôre a CEO/business owner, you will always have these problems] \n \nùóßùóµùóºùòÇùó¥ùóµùòÅ ùó£ùóÆùóøùòÅùóªùó≤ùóø ùó§ùòÇùó≤ùòÄùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùüÆ: \n‚Ü≥  What new topics or skills would help you crush your current business goals? Knowledge that you‚Äôve never found the time to learn. \n \n[Tip: Add these topics & skills to the above list] \n \nTraditionally, you would‚Äôve brought in an expert, to give you specific actionable improvements. \n \nYou still might need to do that. \n \nBut now, you will have a list to start before going to someone. \n \nI call the list: ‚ÄúAI Thought Partner Starter List‚Äù. \n \n*** \n \nThis becomes the starting point now.  \n \nYou can use the attached list as an example :) \n \nPre-AI world, you would never find the time to research any of them.  \n \nNow, with AI, you can make progress with ALL of them! \n \n*** \n \nCan you immediately think of any opportunities? \n \nPut them in the comments! \n \nWould love to brainstorm how we can use AI to take them forward :) \n\"",
