    "title": "ChatGPT/Claude vs Custom-built AI Software: \"\n\" \"\n\"How to know when...",
    "date": "2024-03-07",
    "content": "ChatGPT/Claude vs Custom-built AI Software: \"\n \nHow to know when you‚Äôre ready for ‚ÄúAI as Electricity‚Äù? \n \nThe primary purpose of AI is to help you get from point A to point B, 10x faster. \n \nOur game plan: \n‚Üí Accurately identify where you are (point A).  \n‚Üí Clarify where you want to go (point B).  \n‚Üí Then, use AI to turbocharge your journey towards the goal. \n \nHence, if you haven‚Äôt crystallized points A & B, take a step back before you move forward :) \n \n*** \n \nNow, assuming you have clarity on your goals, here‚Äôs what I recommend: \n \n1/ Start using ChatGPT/Claude and push it as far as you can. \n \n‚Üí  Break down the goal into micro tasks (the smaller the better) \n‚Üí  Write prompts to train ChatGPT/Claude \n‚Üí  Give feedback & specific examples \n‚Üí  Build the habit of working with AI \n \nUsing AI effectively is an art. \n \nAnd ChatGPT/Claude are wonderful to get you started.  \n \n \n2/ Once you‚Äôve found a good groove, start optimizing the new process with custom-built AI software \n \nIf you find yourself: \n \n‚Üí  Doing repetitive manual tasks  \n‚Üí  Piping data through same repositories \n‚Üí  Using the same prompts again and again \n \nEssentially, you‚Äôve pushed the limit, but now you want to take it up a notch. \n \nThat‚Äôs when custom-built AI solutions (‚Äúartisanal software‚Äù) come into the picture. \n \n*** \n \nUsing ChatGPT/Claude, we first find the signal. \n \nThen, custom-built AI solutions double down on that signal. \n \n\"And following this process, you transition from the old-school traditional mode of business to AI-Powered mode of business :)",
