    "content": "I built a custom AI software to automate the creation of first drafts of CRM entries for a client. \"\n \nHere‚Äôs a breakdown of the project: \n \nüò£ What was the problem? \n \nThe client‚Äôs team was spending a significant amount of time: \n‚Üí Taking notes during calls \n‚Üí Drafting internal documents \n‚Üí Manually entering notes into their CRM system. \n \nThis was draining their energy and taking time away from more strategic tasks. \n \nüñ• How did we solve the problem with AI? \n \nCustom AI software emerged as a powerful solution. \n \nThe software worked like this: \nInput ‚Üí Call transcripts, shared documents, expert comments \nProcessing ‚Üí Converted the information into the required format \nOutput ‚Üí Curated & Formatted CRM entries  \n \nEach draft was ~80% (or more) of the way there, with only minor adjustments needed before publication. \nSometimes the entire AI output was good enough that it could be copied and pasted right into the CRM. \n \nüìà What was the Effect? \n \nIf I do the napkin math: \n‚Ü≥ With every iteration, they saved around 15-30 mins \n‚Ü≥ Since August 2023, they‚Äôve used the application to streamline CRM entry (and other, similar, clerical tasks) ~500 times \n‚Ü≥ In total, they‚Äôve saved 125-250 hours! \n \nThat‚Äôs over a month of work! \nIncredible, isn‚Äôt it? \n \nThere‚Äôs an ‚ÄúOpening Pandora‚Äôs box‚Äù feeling that AI can give you once you experience its true power. \n \nTeam members from the client‚Äôs company cannot think of going back now. \n \nThat‚Äôs the magic of being AI-Powered. \n \n*** \n \nP.S. 2 slots are still open for my AI integration program. If you: \n \n‚Üí Resonate with all of the above  \n‚Üí Have an established offer for your business  \n‚Üí Have specific problems that you feel can be instantly automated with AI \n \nCustom-built AI software solutions might be THE thing for you! \n \n\"Just DM me ‚ÄúAI coach‚Äù and I‚Äôll get in touch :)",
