    "title": "Old School Business Owners: \"\n\" \"\n\"Imagine a traditional industrial...",
    "date": "2024-02-28",
    "content": "Old School Business Owners: \"\n \nImagine a traditional industrial factory‚Äî \n \n‚Üí Busy, bustling, but with lots of manual hard labor  \n‚Üí 100s of people, drenched in sweat, working in the heat. \n‚Üí Humans are doing everything, even the smallest of tasks. \n‚Üí Everyone is exhausted, toiling. \n‚Üí Work feels like Work. \n \nNobody has time for innovation. \nThe factory cranks out the same stuff for years and years on razor-thin margins. \nIf they survive, that‚Äôs a Win. \n \nAI-Powered Business Owners: \n \nImagine an advanced, electricity-run factory ‚Äî \n \n‚Ü≥ Clean, humming, super-focused, and hyper-productive. \n‚Ü≥ Machines and robots are working 24*7 x 365. \n‚Ü≥ Clerical tasks are a thing of the past. \nHumans do what only humans can do:  \n‚Ü≥ Thinking, Creating, Relating & Orchestrating. \n‚Ü≥ Work feels like Play. \n \nThis factory is constantly innovating, introducing new product lines & buzzing with ever-increasing margins. \nThe goal is to push the limits and make progress on the frontier. \nProfits are just a by-product. \n \n\"You know which image excites me :)",
