    "content": "How do I identify use cases for ‚ÄúAI as an eager Assistant‚Äù?\"\n\"\nHere‚Äôs the question I ask:\n\"\n‚Üí What activities (that I perform daily) would I delegate if I found the right person?\nOR\n‚Üí What activities (that I perform daily) do I consistently find at #2-3 on my to-do list?\nOR\n‚Üí What activities (that I perform daily) do I find draining but I just HAVE to do for the business?\n\"\n\"\nIf you‚Äôre still going blank, here are 3 most common use cases I‚Äôve seen:\n\"\nùü≠) ùó°ùóºùòÅùó≤-ùòÅùóÆùó∏ùó∂ùóªùó¥ & ùó†ùó≤ùó≤ùòÅùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùó¶ùòÇùó∫ùó∫ùóÆùóøùó∂ùó≤ùòÄ:\nNever take notes in meetings. Always ask AI to do that.\n\"\nThis allows you to be hyper-attentive and make more valuable contributions in the meeting.\n\"\nSubscribe to Otter.ai or Read AI \n\"\nYour meetings will be tidy & organized forever.\n\"\nùüÆ) ùóúùóªùó≥ùóºùóøùó∫ùóÆùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª ùó•ùó≤ùòÅùóøùó∂ùó≤ùòÉùóÆùóπ:\nAsk your assistant to search for the best books, concepts, and frameworks to solve a particular problem.\n\"\nJust specify the context, talk about the problem & ask AI to give you curated information.\n\"\nùôéùôñùô¢ùô•ùô°ùôö ùòæùôùùôñùô©ùôÇùôãùôè ùô•ùôßùô§ùô¢ùô•ùô©: ‚ÄúHey! I have to run a weekly review meeting with my Marketing team. We are working on our first Linkedin campaign. Can you give me some questions to plan my meeting ? I want to understand the status & then be crystal clear on priorities‚Äù\n\"\nùüØ) ùó†ùó∂ùóªùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùóúùóªùòÄùó∂ùó¥ùóµùòÅùòÄ & ùóîùó∞ùòÅùó∂ùóºùóªùòÄ:\nAsk your assistant to go through a dump of information and dig out pieces that you need.\n\"\nThey might be contrarian insights, immediate actionable, unfair advantages, new strategies, etc.\n\"\nùôéùôñùô¢ùô•ùô°ùôö ùòæùôùùôñùô©ùôÇùôãùôè ùô•ùôßùô§ùô¢ùô•ùô©: ‚ÄúHey! Here‚Äôs the transcript of a brainstorming call I had with my marketing team. I want you to go through this and give me all the different strategies we discussed in a table format. Add the potential benefits & roadblocks we discussed. Also give me a list of actions that we identified.‚Äù\n\"\nAnd if you want to take it to the next level,\n\"\nùôéùôñùô¢ùô•ùô°ùôö ùòæùôùùôñùô©ùôÇùôãùôè ùô•ùôßùô§ùô¢ùô•ùô©: ‚ÄúHey! That‚Äôs great. Now act as my trusted advisor coach and highlight blind spots. How could the meeting have gone better? Come up with hard-hitting follow up questions for the team that would invite everyone to elevate quality of ideas in the next follow up session.‚Äù\n\"\n***\n\"\nThese are the simplest ways you can start experimenting with AI.\n\"\nRemember,\nIt only takes one good use case for you to feel the power of AI.\n\"\nThen you won‚Äôt be able to stop thinking of use cases.\n\"\n***\nPS ‚Äì If you‚Äôre looking for a full crash course to get up to speed with AI, I created this specifically for you:\n\"\nstartusingai.carrd.co\n\"\n\"After this course, you‚Äôll know all secrets of the top 1% of AI users.",
