    "content": "I have started using Midjourney as a visioning tool to enhance my goal-setting process.\"\n\"\nInstead of the usual 4x4 OKR slide with text and charts, I've now grounded my weekly sync in an Apple Note, headlined with this image.\n\"\nIt's mobile friendly, so I can walk a few miles and talk through what I've learned over the past week and consider paths forward.\n\"\nI record the whole thing via the Otter.ai iOS app and pop the transcript into Anthropic's Claude Pro at the end, asking it to help me generate additional ideas in re how to address the obstacles I've encountered in my monologue.\n\"\nThe image contains lots of symbols related to my overall strategy, and returning to it helps me focus at the beginning of the session. I have found it especially compelling versus rote text.\n\"\nBuilding a business, especially when you're only accountable to yourself and your clients (in my case, 90% of whom I'm exclusively serve remotely), can be hard.\n\"\n\"These tools make it easier, and I'm grateful for them.",
