    "date": "2024-01-30",
    "content": "My typical daily AI routine:\"\n\"\n7:00 AM - Wake up and avoid screens for the first 30 minutes.\n‚Ü≥ It's a time for me to connect with my family and myself, without the digital world intruding.\n\"\n8:00 AM - Dive into strategic work.\n‚Ü≥ Here, I leverage AI for planning and reflection. I record my thoughts on Otter.ai or Scribe while I run through my structured OKR reflection process. \n\"\nThen I ask Claude to generate insights and follow-up questions. By the end, I‚Äôve reviewed objectives, progress, confidence ratings, and lessons learned.\n\"\n10:00 AM - Client engagements and workshops.\n‚Ü≥ Preparation is key, and I use AI to significantly enhance the quality of my meetings. I upload relevant context (transcripts, goals, priorities) into Claude & collaborate with it to prepare for meetings. It‚Äôs super effective!\n\"\n1:00 PM - Post-meeting follow-ups.\n‚Ü≥ I use Otter to summarize key points and share insights with relevant parties, ensuring that everyone is on the same page.\n\"\n2:00 PM - Afternoons involve reviewing notifications and emails.\n‚Ü≥ Here, I use AI dictation tools to make my communications quick and efficient. I‚Äôve increased my productivity dramatically by combining Whisper & ChatGPT.\n\"\nHere‚Äôs how it works:\n1/ I open all threads, emails & open loops and dictate my answers to Whisper.\n2/ I give ChatGPT this prompt:\n‚ÄúPlease take the transcript above and add whitespace in line breaks for readability‚Äù\nThe results are insane!\nEmail overwhelm is a relic of the past now. All thanks to AI :)\n\"\n3:30 PM - Podcasts and learning.\n‚Ü≥ I use Snipd for quick summaries of podcasts, helping me stay updated with minimal time investment.\n\"\n5:00 PM - Summarize the day\n‚Ü≥ Engaging with my network and sharing insights on platforms like Twitter, utilizing AI for thoughtful and quick interactions.\n\"\nEvening - Unplugging from technology.\nThis balance is crucial for me. It's about spending quality time with family, reading books,  indulging in hobbies, and just being present.\n\"\nTotal time with AI - Roughly 6 hours.\n\"\nI repeat this process daily, with minor tweaks depending on the day's demands.\n\"\nRoughly 25-30% of my working time revolves around leveraging AI, and the impact spreads across 100% of activities.\n\"\nOverall, the idea is to be intentional with my screen time, and be super efficient while I‚Äôm at it :)\n\"\nWorks pretty well for me.\n\"\n***\n\"\nWant more of my insights on leveling up with AI?\n\"\n‚Üí Follow me\n‚Üí Hit the üîî icon\n\"‚Üí Let‚Äôs become AI-enhanced digital workers",
