    "content": "How I use AI to make better life decisions?\"\n\"\n(by making ChatGPT my thought partner)\n\"\nBetter life decisions come from developing a better thinking process.\n\"\nWhen you cultivate a broad perspective, you identify multiple possible options.\nThis abundance of options leads to creative solutions.\n\"\n\"\nBut the problem is: It‚Äôs not easy to broaden your perspective!\nYou need to:\n‚Üí Find people to talk to who‚Äôve gone through a similar journey\n‚Üí Explore your curiosities in diverse fields of knowledge \n‚Üí Learn from failed experiments\n\"\n\"\nPreviously, this used to take a lot of time.\nBut now, we have access to generative AI (ChatGPT). And it‚Äôs game-changing.\n\"\n\"\nHere are 4 techniques I use to help me broaden my perspective with ChatGPT:\n\"\nùü≠/ ùó¶ùó∞ùó≤ùóªùóÆùóøùó∂ùóº ùó¶ùó∂ùó∫ùòÇùóπùóÆùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª\n‚Ü≥ You could use AI to run through a series of \"If-Then\" narratives based on your current decisions. This could involve career moves, educational opportunities, or personal growth strategies.\n\"\nGiven my current role and skills in [your field], if I pursue an advanced degree in [desired field], what potential career paths could open up for me?\n\"\n\"\nùüÆ/ ùóñùóπùóÆùóøùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùó¨ùóºùòÇùóø ùó©ùóÆùóπùòÇùó≤ùòÄ\n‚Ü≥ AI can help you align your decisions with your core values.\n\"\nI value honesty, innovation, and empathy.\nI‚Äôm going through a transition phase with lots of changes happening. Here‚Äôs a description:\n[Give context by explaining the situation that you‚Äôre currently facing]\nCan you help me identify decisions in my professional life that align with these values?\n\"\n[Pro Tip] If you‚Äôre not sure about your core values, take Ben Sands ‚ÄúValue Assessment‚Äù diagnostic test. \nUpload the report and witness how ChatGPT gives you beautiful angles to think about your life decisions :)\n\"\n\"\nùüØ/ ùóñùóøùó∂ùòÅùó∂ùó∞ùóÆùóπ ùó•ùó≤ùó≥ùóπùó≤ùó∞ùòÅùó∂ùóºùóª\n‚Ü≥ Engage with AI to question and challenge your assumptions.\n\"\nI believe that moving to a new city will improve my career prospects.\nHere‚Äôs why: [Speak about your situation and explain your reasoning]\nCan you challenge this assumption and propose situations where this might not be the case?\n\"\n\"\nùü∞/ ùó†ùó≤ùóªùòÅùóÆùóπ ùó†ùóºùó±ùó≤ùóπ ùó®ùóΩùó±ùóÆùòÅùó≤ùòÄ\n‚Ü≥ Allow AI to present new information that changes your perspectives.\n\"\n‚ÄúI'm considering a move to a new city for a job that seems like a great fit for my career goals.\nHere‚Äôs why: [Speak about your situation and explain your reasoning]\nPlease provide data on the quality of life, cost of living, and career growth opportunities in [target city] compared to my current location.\nAre there potential downsides I may not have considered?\nWhat strategies could I employ to mitigate possible challenges associated with this move?\n\"\n\"\nHave a genuine dialogue, treating ChatGPT as a trusted confidant.\n\"\nIt‚Äôll give you something to think about. I promise :)\n\"\n\"Would you like me to expand on any of these?",
