    "title": "How to write a good ChatGPT prompt? \"\n\" \"\n\"(that gives good results...",
    "date": "2024-01-24",
    "content": "How to write a good ChatGPT prompt? \"\n \n(that gives good results for ANY use case) \n \nChatGPT is like a recent master‚Äôs grad assistant you‚Äôve hired. \n \nIt‚Äôs super-smart, but also extremely naive. \n \nIt‚Äôll follow instructions & perform tasks very well. \nBut ONLY if you can teach it EXACTLY what needs to be done! \n \nSo how do we train our ChatGPT assistant well? \nWe need 3 elements. \n1/ Context \n2/ Process \n3/ Examples \n \nLet‚Äôs create a good ChatGPT prompt using the 3 elements. \n \n*** \n \n1Ô∏è‚É£ ùóñùóºùóªùòÅùó≤ùòÖùòÅ - ‚Äúùó™ùóµùóº ùóÆùóøùó≤ ùòÜùóºùòÇ & ùó™ùóµùóÆùòÅ ùó∂ùòÄ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùòÅùóÆùòÄùó∏‚Äù \n \n \nYou are Email Copywriter GPT. \nYou are an expert email copywriter with 10+ years of experience. \nI have written Email sequences for my email list. \nYour task is to help me refine the copy & make it better using proven copywriting principles. \n \n \n2Ô∏è‚É£ ùó£ùóøùóºùó∞ùó≤ùòÄùòÄ - ‚ÄúùóõùóºùòÑ ùòÅùóº ùó±ùóº ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùòÅùóÆùòÄùó∏‚Äù \n \nI'm going to give you inputs: \n‚Üí Who is my target audience? \n‚Üí What are the products & services I‚Äôm offering to my clients? \n‚Üí What is my positioning as a business? \n \nYou have to follow these steps: \n1/ Explain your understanding of my business back to me \n2/ Once I‚Äôm happy, I‚Äôll give you the green light. Then you ask me for emails one by one. \n3/ I‚Äôll give you the email \n4/ You have to read the email & give me a detailed breakdown of the email along with actionable advice on where the copy can be improved. \n \n \n \n3Ô∏è‚É£ ùóòùòÖùóÆùó∫ùóΩùóπùó≤ùòÄ - ‚Äúùó™ùóµùóÆùòÅ ùó±ùóºùó≤ùòÄ ùóÆ ùó¥ùóºùóºùó± ùóøùó≤ùòÄùóΩùóºùóªùòÄùó≤ ùóπùóºùóºùó∏ ùóπùó∂ùó∏ùó≤‚Äù \n \nYou must give me your breakdown in the following format. \nRating of the copy (0/10): \nWhy?: \nWhat actionable advice would you give to bump up the rating: \nSpecific sections where these improvements can be implemented: \n1/ \nBefore Section ‚Üí \nAfter Section rewritten with improvement ‚Üí \n2/ \nBefore Section ‚Üí \nAfter Section rewritten with improvement ‚Üí \n \n*** \n \nNo matter what use case, if you write a good prompt‚Äîjust like giving clear directions to that recent Masters grad‚Äîyou will get good responses. \n \nTry it out with different types of problems: those where you know how to do something specific, don‚Äôt want to do it anymore, but it needs to get done regularly. \n \nOnce you start getting into a habit of AI delegation, work becomes efficient & fun! \n \nLet me know if you find something :) \n \n*** \nPS- If you‚Äôre having trouble finding these use cases for your business, I wrote a 5-Day Educational Email course just for you. \n \nIt‚Äôll give you everything you need to start identifying endless opportunities to use AI. \n \n\"Get it here: startusingai.carrd.co",
