    "content": "How I identify endless AI automation use-cases for my clients in <20 mins: \"\n \n(A dead-simple 4-step process) \n \nùü≠. ùóúùó±ùó≤ùóªùòÅùó∂ùó≥ùòÜ ùóñùóπùó∂ùó≤ùóªùòÅ ùóöùóºùóÆùóπùòÄ \n‚Ü≥ I ask: \"If you could wave a magic wand and achieve one major result in 3 months, what would it be?\" This sets the direction for AI integration, which should always be done in light of the CEO‚Äôs strategic intent. \n \nùüÆ. ùóïùòÇùòÄùó∂ùóªùó≤ùòÄùòÄ ùóïùóπùòÇùó≤ùóΩùóøùó∂ùóªùòÅùó∂ùóªùó¥  \n‚Ü≥ Using tools like Miro, I draw an end-to-end map of the company's processes. This helps visualize the workflow, making it easy to identify where AI can be most useful‚Äîin other words, ‚Äúwhere to install the first AI-as-electricity outlet‚Äù. \n \nùüØ. ùóòùòÖùóΩùóπùóºùóøùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùóîùóú ùòÇùòÄùó≤-ùó∞ùóÆùòÄùó≤ùòÄ \n‚Ü≥ We dig out pain points where AI can most effectively (and immediately) streamline operations and eliminate bottlenecks, giving operators their time and energy back. \n \nùü∞. ùóôùó∂ùóªùó±ùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùòÅùóµùó≤ ùóñùóµùóÆùó∫ùóΩùó∂ùóºùóª  \n‚Ü≥I look for an in-house early adopter of AI. Someone who wants to master their craft of AI and sees AI as a tool to help them take things to the next level. They become AI pioneers in the organization. \n \nEvery client session is an opportunity to create that ‚ÄúAha‚Äù moment ‚Äì where we pinpoint the perfect spot for AI to add immediate AND durable value by helping humans delegate mundane tasks to AI.  \n \nThis not only boosts productivity but also ignites a spark of innovation within the company, since, once they‚Äôre no longer burdened with rote clerical trivia, workers become naturally curious and use their surplus energy to find new problems to solve and run creative experiments. \n \nFind 1 application. (Don‚Äôt overthink it!) \n \nStart using AI.  \n \n \nPS ‚Äì As a New Year's giveaway, I‚Äôm doing 10 FREE AI Power Hour consultations. In 20 mins, we‚Äôll follow this exact process to give you an actionable AI roadmap to follow. \n \n \n\"Comment ‚Äúüëçüèªüëçüèªüëçüèª‚Äù and I‚Äôll reach out to you :)",
