    "content": "ü§î Yesterday, my client asked me, ‚ÄúHow the heck do you get so much done?\" \"\n \n‚Üí Teaching business owners how to use AI, \n‚Üí Developing custom AI software for their staff, \n‚Üí Running OKR processes for executives, \n‚Üí Posting consistently on LinkedIn, \n‚Üí Co-chairing the MIT AI Conference, and \n‚Üí Raising twin boys üë¶üë¶ \n \nüîë My secret: I use AI as a *thought partner* to solve complex problems 10x faster than I could without AI. \n \nHere‚Äôs the 3-step process on how to start using AI as your thought partner: \n \nùü≠. ùó®ùòÄùó≤ ùóîùóú ùòÅùóº ùó†ùóÆùó∏ùó≤ ùó¶ùó≤ùóªùòÄùó≤ \n \nNot sure what to do next?  \nBlabber your thoughts & ChatGPT will help you structure your thinking. \n \n‚ÄúHey, I‚Äôm facing a problem, and I need you to help me think. I‚Äôm first going to give you some context. Then I‚Äôm going to tell you what‚Äôs the problem. And then I‚Äôll tell you everything that‚Äôs in my head. You can structure the thinking and help me make sense. Here you go: {Talk about context}, {Talk about problem} {Say everything in your head}‚Äù \n \nùüÆ. ùó®ùòÄùó≤ ùóîùóú ùòÅùóº ùóÆùòÄùó∏ ùòÜùóºùòÇ ùóñùóπùóÆùóøùó∂ùó≥ùòÜùó∂ùóªùó¥ ùó§ùòÇùó≤ùòÄùòÅùó∂ùóºùóªùòÄ \n \nAfter you have structure, it‚Äôll ask you questions to deepen your understanding. \n \n‚ÄùHey, so here is how I‚Äôm thinking about the problem now. I think I‚Äôve come up with an initial hypothesis. So, now I‚Äôm going to tell you my thoughts & you‚Äôll ask me clarifying questions that you have to help me fill in the gaps. Are you ready?  \nHere you go: {Articulate your understanding}‚Äù \n \nùüØ. ùó®ùòÄùó≤ ùóîùóú ùòÅùóº ùóñùóøùó∂ùòÅùó∂ùóæùòÇùó≤ ùòÜùóºùòÇùóø ùó¶ùóºùóπùòÇùòÅùó∂ùóºùóªùòÄ \n \nNow, finally, ask ChatGPT to stress test your ideas. \n \n‚ÄùNow, I want you to bring in 3 experts who are thought-leaders in the field of my problem. Introduce these experts & then tell me what views these experts will have on my solution to the problem. Ask the experts to be clear, concise & actionable.‚Äù \n \n*** \n \nPS: If you‚Äôre wondering... \n \nYES, you need to literally start *talking* to ChatGPT. \n \nThe process isn‚Äôt unlike discussing problems with our friends and trusted advisors. \n \nExcept AI is infinitely patient and ready to work with you at any point. \n \nTry it out! You‚Äôll be surprised at how well it responds. \n \n(especially with the new text-to-speech capabilities that turn it into a live conversation!) üôÇ \n \n\"And let me know how it goes in the DMs/comments.",
