    "content": "Last month, my client cracked a 100% boost in productivity after plugging AI into their business. But this wasn‚Äôt the best part! \"\n \n2 hidden benefits delighted the CEO even more üëáüèª \n \n1. ‚ÄúNo note-taking in 1-1 meetings. It‚Äôs incredibly better to just be present in the conversation and let AI do the typing.‚Äù \n \nTips for CEOs: \n \n‚Üí Install Read.ai/Otter.ai & start transcribing your meetings \n‚Üí Feed the transcript to ChatGPT (or Claude or Otter AI Chat) \n‚Üí Ask ChatGPT to summarize, derive insights, point inconsistencies, identify opportunities, and anything useful. \n‚Üí Give ChatGPT a blank structure + 1 example. It‚Äôll instantly convert the transcript into beautiful meeting notes. \n‚Üí Now you can pay closer attention to the content, observe subtle cues of other attendees, and identify deeper client needs while your assistant does the note-taking. \n \n \n2. ‚ÄúOne person on the team was initially cautious & afraid. Now she‚Äôs like, this is tremendous.‚Äù \n \nTips for CEOs: \n \n‚Üí Identify 1 activity that is central to operations but is tedious to perform manually \n‚Üí Figure out the information flow: Input ‚Üí Process ‚Üí Output \n‚Üí Explain this process to ChatGPT and provide 3-4 varied examples \n‚Üí Try your ChatGPT prompts & give feedback to make it better \n‚Üí Make a video on Loom to explain your process to the team \n \nOnce your team starts using AI, they‚Äôll be happier & more productive.  \n \nOr, as my client says: \n‚ÄúPandora‚Äôs box has been opened now & I can‚Äôt go back‚Äù \n \n*** \nI specialize in integrating AI into your Business to help you save time, grow revenues & beat the competition. 2 slots have just opened up in my schedule. \n \nWho I work with: \n‚Üí SMB Business Owners with Remote Teams (10-200 employees) \n \n\"If you want the AI transformation, DM me ‚ÄúAI‚Äù and we‚Äôll have a quick chat!",
