    "title": "When technology suddenly starts doing *absurd* stuff, it‚Äôs a sign t...",
    "date": "2023-11-29",
    "content": "When technology suddenly starts doing *absurd* stuff, it‚Äôs a sign that things are about to change! \"\n \nIt‚Äôs in those first magic moments with a revolutionary technology that you realize something special is about to happen. \n \nThink: Web Browser in 1993, AI in 2022. \n \nIt‚Äôs when you realize that something that was literally impossible now suddenly becomes possible. \n \nFor example, in just 4‚Äì5 minutes, I can create a custom commercial for your company, where your latest and greatest product line gets pitched by your favorite actor. \n \n(I recently did this during a live client workshop with...Ryan Reynolds.)  \n \n*** \n \nüìå¬†[Here‚Äôs the secret recipe for the magic show] \n \n‚Üí Take all copy from your company website \n‚Üí Copy the transcript of a Ryan Reynolds commercial \n‚Üí Paste it all into a ChatGPT chat \n‚Üí Use AI to clone Ryan‚Äôs voice in just a few clicks via ElevenLabs \n‚Üí Create images using Midjourney and FaceSwapID \n‚Üí Turn the images into videos using D-ID, Kaiber, and RunwayML \n‚Üí Edit the video & add subtitles using Descript \n‚Üí As a bonus: add a custom soundtrack with MusicGen \n \n*** \n \n‚ö°Ô∏è The advent of generative AI is truly a zero-to-one moment. \n \nIt‚Äôs making something that was previously impossible, possible.  \n \nPeople routinely expect incremental improvements, like a 20-30% boost in efficiency.  \n \nBut in truth, infinite improvements are possible for some tasks because you‚Äôre dividing by zero. \n \nWe can now do things we could not imagine before. \n \nThat‚Äôs incredible! \n \n*** \nüí° And that‚Äôs the point behind the Ryan Reynolds commercial. \n \nDo we use it for our marketing? \n \n‚Üí Definitely not ‚Äî¬†but it certainly gets the creative gears turning‚Ä¶ \n \nI love sharing these magic moments with clients in real-time to demonstrate that AI can open up entirely new possibilities for their business. \n \nThings that we couldn‚Äôt even imagine before! \n \nSo, set ambitious goals and start experimenting with AI. \n \n\"You never know when you‚Äôll stumble onto a massive breakthrough :)",
