    "id": "post-2023-11-27-7134828261271838720",
    "title": "My first breakthrough with AI happened way back in 2016",
    "date": "2023-11-27",
    "content": "My first breakthrough with AI happened way back in 2016. \"\n \nü§î So, what did I do? \n \nI was on the data analytics team at Red Bull Media House. \n \nAnd I was helping executives make sense of billions of data points captured from our video applications. \n \nThen one day, on a plane, I had an idea: \n \n‚ÄúWe can use computers and cloud services not only to analyze the data but also to enhance the product itself. And we can use AWS Rekognition to help speed up the process of video metadata tagging (which was very labor intensive)!‚Äù \n \nSo, I paid for Wi-fi on the plane, crunched the code & published the prototype with some cost calculations on the company wiki. \n \nIt was a cool idea, and I enjoyed doing it. \n \nBut nothing came out of it. \n \n Until months later, while at MIT, a friend from Red Bull gave me a call and said, laughing, \n \n‚ÄùYour name came up in a meeting today.‚Äù \n \n‚ÄúOh, yeah?‚Äù I said. \n \n‚ÄúYeah ‚Äî they were talking about how before you left for grad school, you tried to send robots to take their jobs!‚Äù  \n \nThat‚Äôs when I understood what it‚Äôs like to really operate at the frontier. \n \n*** \n \nüí´ Looking back today: \n \nThis feeling of pushing the boundaries & building brand-new technology FAST is what excited me the most.  \n \nAnd it still does! \n \nIt pushes me to stretch the boundaries of what‚Äôs possible with my clients. \n \nAnd it‚Äôs what drives me to devise innovative AI solutions for business owners across a variety of industries & applications! \n \n*** \n \nüïµüèª So, if you‚Äôre curious about how you can start using AI, I have a special gift for you.  \n \nBased on insights from 20+ AI integration projects, I‚Äôve built an Email Crash Course that specifically teaches beginners on how to get started with AI for business. \n \nI‚Äôm launching the course on Friday. \n \n\"Stay tuned!",
