    "date": "2023-08-04",
    "content": "üîÆüíºüß† Where can you start integrating AI into your work to unlock more energy, productivity, and satisfaction?\"\n\"\nI've developed a simple heuristic to answer this question. It involves a journey back through your calendar and a deep dive into your to-do list. The aim? To identify the activities that give you energy and those that drain it from you. Imagine spending 80% of your work week doing what you love while delegating the rest to AI! üöÄ\n\"\nSo, how does it work? ü§î\n\"\n1Ô∏è‚É£ Take a trip through your calendar from the past 1-4 weeks. Identify events that left you feeling energized and vitalized. These are tasks you don't want to delegate. Now imagine doing more of them.\n\"\n2Ô∏è‚É£ Next, identify the events that left you feeling drained. These are ideal candidates for delegation to AI. With the right tools, you can automate up to 80% of these tasks.\n\"\n3Ô∏è‚É£ Finally, identify the tasks that consistently fall to number two on your to-do list. You know the ones I mean - necessary but not particularly rewarding tasks. These too are ripe for AI automation.\n\"\nThis process opens the door to a virtuous cycle. By delegating the draining tasks to AI, you free up resources to focus on the tasks that give you energy. Over time, this leads to increased productivity, satisfaction, and a lot more of your time back! ‚è≥\n\"\nI've encapsulated this process into a handy ChatGPT applet. This AI coach will guide you through this self-discovery journey and help you identify where you can integrate AI into your workflows. The outcome? More time and energy to do the things that truly matter to you.\n\"\nGive it a try! You might surprise yourself with the insights you gain. And once you've taken this journey, why not share a summary of what you learned as a comment on this post?\n\"\nüëâ https://lnkd.in/dRxA4qrG\n\"\nHere's to becoming not just more productive, but happier and more satisfied at work! ü•Ç\n\"\n\"#AIIntegration #Productivity #WorkSatisfaction #ChatGPT #AI",
