    "title": "\"The amount of free leverage available to anyone with a bit of agen...",
    "date": "2023-07-28",
    "content": "The amount of free leverage available to anyone with a bit of agency and a ChatGPT Plus sub is unreal. üöÄ\n\"\nIt's a low hanging fruit free for all out there. üçé\n\"\nI posted this on Twitter (X?), and a curious mind üß† asked me to share some less-known paths to low-hanging AI fruit.\n\"\nüå≥ After months of mind-melding with the machines (and teaching clients how to do the same), here are my top 6 tips:\n\"\n1Ô∏è‚É£ Uploading zips of entire repositories to the code interpreter. It's like having an entire digital product team at your disposal - an expert designer, a senior engineer, and a product manager who can provide concrete feedback on how to take your code to the next level. üè¢üë©‚Äçüíª\n\"\n2Ô∏è‚É£ Bypassing traditional data connectors and reporting layers to create completely custom reports and memos. Dramatically improve insight generation and reporting throughput without waiting days or weeks for a team of analysts or data scientists. Just ask questions in natural language that you're personally curious about and get good information. üí°üìà\n\"\n3Ô∏è‚É£ Open-ended thought partnership conversations with GPT-4 through the iOS whisper feature. It's like having a personal mentor, helping you overcome the blank page/cold start problem when tackling a new project. üó®Ô∏èüëÅÔ∏è\n\"\n4Ô∏è‚É£ Creating system architecture diagrams, based on chunks of a transcript of a live conversation with an end user. With the \"show me\" plugin (my favorite among all the ChatGPT Plus plugins), you can visualize complex structures on the fly. It's like having a live, interactive whiteboard session with an expert. üó£Ô∏èüé®\n\"\n5Ô∏è‚É£ Rapidly iterating through variables for mid-journey prompts by discussing your aesthetic preferences. It's like having an incredibly imaginative thought partner who can help you explore your ideas by translating them into symbols and images that stretch the boundaries of your imagination. üí≠üöÄ\n\"\n6Ô∏è‚É£ Asking GPT-4 to suggest obscure but credible thinkers who have published papers on the precise combination of topics you're currently interested in. It's almost like having a panel of credible experts ready to engage in an impassioned debate to accelerate your journey towards a new pocket at the frontiers of human knowledge. üìöüß™\n\"\nWhat's missing from this list?\n\"\nWhat other low-hanging fruit should more motivated, AI-savvy knowledge workers reach for?\n\"\n\"#ai #artificialintelligence",
