    "date": "2023-05-09",
    "content": "Suppose you have a thorny or time-intensive problem. In that case, I highly recommend you ask Christian to perform a workshop to demonstrate the power of AI to provide solutions and make your professional and intellectual life more productive.\n\"\nEugene Procknow, thank you for the kind words!\n\"\nI had the pleasure of working with Gene last week as part of one of my \"AI on-ramp workshops\" (link below to sign up).\n\"\nWe covered:\n\"\n- how to stimulate creativity and \"write\" with AI\n- using AI to simulate conversations between experts\n- chatting with PDFs using Bing\n- being careful with LLM-outputted information (hallucinations are still a problem!)\n- ...and more!\n\"\n\"If you want to turbo-charge your workflow, get more done, and feel confident in your ability to use AI on a daily basis, you can sign up for a private AI workshop here: https://lnkd.in/gCfawbdm",
