    "content": "I sometimes struggle with making my writing digestible on social media...\"\n\"\nSO, I took this as a challenge and gave GPT-4 the task of translating the insights from my latest piece about the \"relocalization of software\" into an \"explain like I'm 5\" format that uses \"characters from popular media.\n\"\nIn a few clicks, and with the help of¬†@D-ID¬†,¬†@Runway¬†,¬†@Midjourney¬†and¬†@ElevenLabs, it produced the script (and image prompts) for an explainer, narrated by Captain America ü§Ø\n\"\nOriginal piece I wrote: https://lnkd.in/eNvs_xFi\n\"\nPS ‚Äî¬†I wrote the piece from scratch (first draft via voice dictation), edited it w/ assistance from ChatGPT and Grammarly, and created the video all today, w/ less than 2 hours total labor.\n\"\n\"If nothing else, AI can already turbo-charge productivity!",
