    "title": "The way we think of best practices in the business world is about t...",
    "date": "2022-12-20",
    "content": "The way we think of best practices in the business world is about to change‚Äîand not just a little, but drastically.\"\n\"\nArtificial intelligence is set to revolutionize the sales profession, transforming the way companies approach best practices and breaking the traditional methods that have been established for decades.\n\"\nAI has the capability to dramatically reduce the cost of experimentation and simulation in order to find new strategies for achieving a particular goal. This means that, in the context of sales, the processes around building rapport, probing for pain, finding a decision-making unit, and uncovering a prospect's willingness to pay could all be disrupted and transformed by AI.¬†\n\"\nThis is because certain AI algorithms, developed by researchers at DeepMind, Meta, and other institutions for the purpose of winning certain games (e.g., Go, Poker, Diplomacy) have proven extremely successful in running simulations of AI playing itself that cover a much broader range than had ever been considered by traditional master players.\n\"\nThis has exposed previously unknown pockets of abstract space, unthought-of strategies, and more optimal solutions that have had much better results.\n\"\nWhat does this mean for the business world?\n\"\nAs an example, companies collecting high-fidelity recordings of every conversation, video chat, etc. between their salespeople and prospects can create AI agents that are virtual representations of their salespeople and simulate interactions to explore a much wider possibility space. This will likely lead to discoveries of new strategies that break the rules of best practices and completely transform the sales profession.¬†\n\"\nAI can also be used to enhance the innovation process by bringing down the cost of simulation and experimentation. So don't hesitate‚Äîbuckle up and lean into it!\n\"\nRecord everything and start thinking about how you can use AI to your advantage...\n\"\nThis could be the difference between staying competitive and being left behind in the ever-changing business world.\n\"\n\"#artificialintelligence #ai #sales #innovation #digitaltransformation",
