    "id": "post-2022-12-14-7008869348614320128",
    "title": "Wondering if you're ready to use AI like ChatGPT?\"\n\"\"\n\"You are, and...",
    "date": "2022-12-14",
    "content": "Wondering if you're ready to use AI like ChatGPT?\"\n\"\nYou are, and here's how...\n\"\nTreat it like a first-year analyst.\n\"\nScope a problem, give context, and ask for 5 versions of something: a workshop agenda, a series of cold outreach emails, a presentation outline.\n\"\nGive it rounds of feedback (\"I like version X...how about you add some more of Y?\") until you like what you see.\n\"\nOpenAI's #ChatGPT is like a DM thread w a recent college grad who‚Äôs working for free and eager to please.\n\"\nUsing #AI to produce boilerplate that fits your needs frees up your invaluable attention to focus on more creative and cognitively demanding tasks.\n\"\nTry it now!\n\"\n\"http://chat.openai.com",
