    "date": "2022-11-28",
    "content": "Next time you reach for your phone, pause and ask yourself, ‚ÄúWhat am I really looking for?‚Äù\"\n\"\nWhen we‚Äôre bored, we take stock of our pasts and plan for the future.\n\"\nBut in an age of digital distraction, boredom is in short supply‚Äîno wonder it often feels like we‚Äôre stuck in an eternal present.\n\"\nThe key to thriving in the superabundant digital age is not to use technology to do more with less, but rather to do less but better.\n\"\nExcellent words of wisdom from Manoush Zomorodi !\n\"\n\" #technology #digital #attention",
