    "content": "Want to learn how VC-backed founders manage their time and stay focused?\"\n\"\nListen in to an expert panel of entrepreneurs & MIT Sloan School of Management alumni on the evening of Monday the 28th via the new LinkedIn audio event feature.\n\"\n40m for panel discussion and 20m for Q&A.\n\"\nAdd üî• questions about time & attention management in the comments below, and we'll make sure they get answered live by panelists!\n\"\n\"#management #entrepreneurs #founders #timemanagement",
